graph TD
    A["Load & Preprocess Data
    emissions-data/*.csv
    Extracts hourly carbon intensity from CSV files 2021-2025"]

    A --> B["Engineer Features
    Creates cyclical features: hour_sin/cos dayofyear_sin/cos
    Captures daily cycles and seasonal patterns"]

    B --> C["Normalize Data
    StandardScaler
    Prevents large values from dominating learning"]

    C --> D["Create Time Windows
    Input: 24h historical data
    Output: 24h forecast target
    Sliding window across time series"]

    D --> E["CNN Model"]

    E --> F["Conv1D 64 filters → Conv1D 32 filters
    Detects 3-hour patterns and combines them
    Flatten → Dense 128 → Dense 64
    Learns complex relationships with Dropout 30%
    Output 24 neurons for 24-hour forecast"]

    F --> G["Train & Save
    Optimizer: Adam LR=0.001
    Loss: MSE, 50 epochs, batch_size=32"]

    G --> H["carbon_model_cnn_v3.tflite
    Lightweight model ~2-5MB
    Runs on mobile and edge devices"]
    G --> I["scaler_params_cnn_v3.json
    Saves mean and scale for
    denormalizing predictions"]
    G --> J["model_params.json
    Config: window_size=24
    forecast_horizon=24, features list"]

    H --> K["Deploy Model
    Step 1: Collect last 24h data
    Step 2: Normalize using scaler params"]
    I --> K

    K --> L["Normalize Input Data
    Last 24h hourly values
    Apply mean and scale from JSON"]

    L --> M["TFLite Inference
    Run model on normalized input
    Get 24 scaled predictions"]

    M --> N["Denormalize Output
    Using target_scaler params
    Convert -3 to +3 back to real values"]

    N --> O["Carbon Intensity Forecast
    gCO₂eq/kWh for next 24 hours"]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style E fill:#f3e5f5
    style H fill:#fff3e0
    style O fill:#c8e6c9